  <description type="morphology">Plants small, pale green to dull green, sometimes yellowish. Stems 2–6 cm, creeping, subjulaceous, irregularly branched to somewhat pinnate. Leaves straight to somewhat falcate, oblong-lanceolate, gradually narrowed to apex; margins nearly entire; alar cells many, subquadrate; &lt;laminal cells 60–80 × 3–4 µm (or slightly larger)&gt;. Branch leaves 1–1.4 × 0.2–0.4 mm or slightly smaller.</description>
